OL,3,CCommunities urged to create emergency
OL,4,Cplans after record rainfall
OL,6,FPeople in East Devon are being urged
OL,7,Fto create emergency response plans in
OL,8,Fcase of extreme weather.
OL,10,FSevere weather across the district in
OL,11,Fthe past 18 months has caused several
OL,12,Fnotable incidents, including flash
OL,13,Ffloods in the Otter Valley in May
OL,14,F2023, and Storm Ciaran in November,
OL,15,Fwhich damaged Exmouth's sea wall.
