OL,3,CCommunities urged to create emergency
OL,4,Cplans after record rainfall
OL,6,FMatt Blythe, who helps oversee
OL,7,Fenvironment and climate change-related
OL,8,Factivities at East Devon District
OL,9,FCouncil, said Met Office data showed
OL,10,FEngland recently experienced the
OL,11,Fwettest 18-month period since 1836.
OL,13,FHe said this had contributed to some
OL,14,Fof the recent events in the district,
OL,15,Fand showed the need to be prepared.
OL,17,F"There's a lot of unseen, back-office
OL,18,Fwork required for these type of plans
OL,19,Fand we have had a couple of relatively
OL,20,Flarge events," he said.
