OL,3,CCommunities urged to create emergency
OL,4,Cplans after record rainfall
OL,6,F"We had around 400 weather message
OL,7,Fwarnings in the 2023/24 financial
OL,8,Fyear, and we are trying to get those
OL,9,Fout to staff and officers so they are
OL,10,Faware if they are out and about in the
OL,11,Fdistrict.
OL,13,F"We also send them on to parish and
OL,14,Ftown clerks, especially for amber
OL,15,Fwarnings and above, to help ensure
OL,16,Fwe're communicating as widely as
OL,17,Fpossible."
OL,19,FSeveral councillors said they are
OL,20,Falready involved in creating emergency
OL,21,Fplans in their own communities.
