OL,6,FCllr Geoff Jung (Liberal Democrat,
OL,7,FWoodbury and Lymptone), portfolio
OL,8,Fholder for coast, country and
OL,9,Fenvironment said: "Anything we can do
OL,10,Fto encourage communities that don't
OL,11,Fhave a plan like this to create one is
OL,12,Fworth doing.
OL,14,F"I run my own community resilience
OL,15,Fgroup in my village and I go to a lot
OL,16,Fof the meetings, and any community
OL,17,Fthat could have problems with flooding
OL,18,Freally needs to have a group set up so
OL,19,Fit can react when a flood happens."
