OL,6,FHe added: "If there are 20 or 30
OL,7,Fcommunities flooded, the fire brigade
OL,8,Fcan't get to everyone, so people have
OL,9,Fto work with what they have got and
OL,10,Fhaving a community resilience group
OL,11,Fwith a plan, and people who know what
OL,12,Fto and when, really does work."
OL,14,FIt is thought that roughly 60 East
OL,15,FDevon communities have such plans, but
OL,16,Fscrutiny committee vice chair Cllr
OL,17,FDuncan Mackinder (Liberal Democrat,
OL,18,FYarty) proposed a motion that
OL,19,Fcommunities without resilience plans
OL,20,Fbe encouraged to create them.
